others,"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add their wrongdoing"},{"kind":"text","text":" your Father will not forgive your offenses."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add their wrongdoing"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Whenever you fast, don’t be gloomy like the hypocrites. For they disfigure their faces"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Is 58:5","book":"Isa","chapter":58,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:35","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":35,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:13","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" so that their fasting is obvious to people. Truly I tell you, they have their reward. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Is 58:5","book":"Isa","chapter":58,"verse":5},{"label":"Mt 18:35","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":35},{"label":"Jms 2:13","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":13}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But when you fast, put oil on your head and wash your face,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ru 3:3","book":"Rut","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Sm 12:20","book":"2Sa","chapter":12,"verse":20,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dn 10:3","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":3,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ru 3:3","book":"Rut","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"2Sm 12:20","book":"2Sa","chapter":12,"verse":20},{"label":"Dn 10:3","book":"Dan","chapter":10,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"so that your fasting isn’t obvious to others but to your Father who is in secret. And your Father who sees in secret will reward you."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss add openly"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss add openly"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Don’t store up for yourselves treasures"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or valuables"},{"kind":"text","text":" on earth, where moth and rust destroy and where thieves break in and steal."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Pr 23:4","book":"Pro","chapter":23,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Heb 13:5","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":5,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Pr 23:4","book":"Pro","chapter":23,"verse":4},{"label":"Heb 13:5","book":"Heb","chapter":13,"verse":5}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or valuables"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:20","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But store up for yourselves treasures in heaven,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:21","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":21,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:33","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":33,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 18:22","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":22,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 6:19","book":"1Ti","chapter":6,"verse":19,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" where neither moth nor rust destroys, and where thieves don’t break in and steal. "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 19:21","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":21},{"label":"Lk 12:33","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":33},{"label":"Lk 18:22","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":22},{"label":"1Tm 6:19","book":"1Ti","chapter":6,"verse":19}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:21","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For where your treasure is, there your heart will be also."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:22","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“The eye is the lamp of the body. If your eye is healthy, your whole body will be full of light. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:23","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But if your eye is bad, your whole body will be full of darkness. So if the light within you is darkness, how deep is that darkness!"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 4:16","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":16,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:12","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":12,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:13","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":13,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 25:30","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":30,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 27:45","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":45,"letter":"e"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 4:16","book":"Mat","chapter":4,"verse":16},{"label":"Mt 8:12","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":12},{"label":"Mt 22:13","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":13},{"label":"Mt 25:30","book":"Mat","chapter":25,"verse":30},{"label":"Mt 27:45","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":45}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:24","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“No one can serve two masters, since either he will hate one and love the other, or he will be devoted to one and despise the other. You cannot serve both God and money."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 16:13","book":"Luk","chapter":16,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 1:10","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 4:4","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":4,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 16:13","book":"Luk","chapter":16,"verse":13},{"label":"Gl 1:10","book":"Gal","chapter":1,"verse":10},{"label":"Jms 4:4","book":"Jas","chapter":4,"verse":4}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:25","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Therefore I tell you:"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 12:22–31","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":22,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":" Don’t worry about your life, what you will eat or what you will drink; or about your body, what you will wear. Isn’t life more than food and the body more than clothing?"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:41","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":41,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:6","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":7,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lk 12:22–31","book":"Luk","chapter":12,"verse":22},{"label":"Lk 10:41","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":41},{"label":"Php 4:6","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":6},{"label":"1Pt 5:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Consider the birds of the sky: They don’t sow or reap or gather into barns, yet your heavenly Father feeds them. Aren’t you worth more than they?"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 38:41","book":"Job","chapter":38,"verse":41,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ps 147:9","book":"Psa","chapter":147,"verse":9,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 10:29–31","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":29,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 38:41","book":"Job","chapter":38,"verse":41},{"label":"Ps 147:9","book":"Psa","chapter":147,"verse":9},{"label":"Mt 10:29–31","book":"Mat","chapter":10,"verse":29}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Can any of you add one moment to his life span"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Or add a single cubit to his height"},{"kind":"text","text":" by worrying? "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Or add a single cubit to his height"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"And why do you worry about clothes? Observe how the wildflowers of the field grow: They don’t labor or spin thread. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:29","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Yet I tell you that not even Solomon in all his splendor was adorned like one of these. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:30","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"If that’s how God clothes the grass of the field, which is here today and thrown into the furnace tomorrow, won’t he do much more for you —you of little faith?"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 10:4","book":"1Ki","chapter":10,"verse":4,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 8:26","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":26,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 14:31","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":31,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 16:8","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":8,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"1Kg 10:4","book":"1Ki","chapter":10,"verse":4},{"label":"Mt 8:26","book":"Mat","chapter":8,"verse":26},{"label":"Mt 14:31","book":"Mat","chapter":14,"verse":31},{"label":"Mt 16:8","book":"Mat","chapter":16,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:31","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"So don’t worry, saying, ‘What will we eat?’ or ‘What will we drink?’ or ‘What will we wear?’ "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:32","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For the Gentiles eagerly seek all these things, and your heavenly Father knows that you need them. "}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:33","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But seek first the kingdom of God"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss omit of God"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 1:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":1,"verse":15,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 20:25","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" and his righteousness,"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 27:19","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":19,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 7:29","book":"Luk","chapter":7,"verse":29,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 23:41","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":41,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 23:47","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":47,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 5:30","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":30,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 17:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":25,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 3:14","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":14,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"text","text":" and all these things will be provided for you."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Kg 3:13","book":"1Ki","chapter":3,"verse":13,"letter":"j"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 19:28","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":28,"letter":"k"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:29","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":29,"letter":"l"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 18:29","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":29,"letter":"m"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Tm 4:8","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":8,"letter":"n"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 1:15","book":"Mrk","chapter":1,"verse":15},{"label":"Ac 20:25","book":"Act","chapter":20,"verse":25},{"label":"Mt 27:19","book":"Mat","chapter":27,"verse":19},{"label":"Lk 7:29","book":"Luk","chapter":7,"verse":29},{"label":"Lk 23:41","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":41},{"label":"Lk 23:47","book":"Luk","chapter":23,"verse":47},{"label":"Jn 5:30","book":"Jhn","chapter":5,"verse":30},{"label":"Jn 17:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":17,"verse":25},{"label":"Ac 3:14","book":"Act","chapter":3,"verse":14},{"label":"1Kg 3:13","book":"1Ki","chapter":3,"verse":13},{"label":"Mt 19:28","book":"Mat","chapter":19,"verse":28},{"label":"Mk 10:29","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":29},{"label":"Lk 18:29","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":29},{"label":"1Tm 4:8","book":"1Ti","chapter":4,"verse":8}],"footnotes":[{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss omit of God"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:6:34","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Therefore don’t worry about tomorrow, because tomorrow will worry about itself. Each day has enough trouble"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 6:25","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:41","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":41,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Php 4:6","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":6,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 5:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":7,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"text","text":" of its own."}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 6:25","book":"Mat","chapter":6,"verse":25},{"label":"Lk 10:41","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":41},{"label":"Php 4:6","book":"Php","chapter":4,"verse":6},{"label":"1Pt 5:7","book":"1Pe","chapter":5,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]}]},"cachedAt":1783099495984}